Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.73,0:01:34.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在日本第一山富士山上面
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.57,0:01:39.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目的是要在山顶看日出
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.20,0:01:43.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在正在向本八合目的山中小屋前进
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.17,0:01:50.33,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(560,430)}富士山 不可小觑…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.84,0:01:58.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.93,0:02:04.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,富士山真的有啊 有种不可思议的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.18,0:02:08.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我懂 我也没有现实感 好像身处在梦境一般
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.15,0:02:12.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在山顶上看的日出更加梦幻哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.65,0:02:13.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.49,0:02:22.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要登上这种地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.54,0:02:27.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这已经算不上是路了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.37,0:02:31.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铁链只是一个引导 不可以抓哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.08,0:02:32.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.51,0:02:40.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是空气太稀薄了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.89,0:02:43.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算待着不动呼吸也很困难
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.89,0:02:52.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八合目 明明刚才起就一直看得见了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.02,0:02:55.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么时候才能到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.65,0:03:00.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没 没事的 这点程度小意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.28,0:03:03.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按照自己的节奏走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.66,0:03:05.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢慢来 慢慢来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.83,0:03:08.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 大家是不是太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.87,0:03:11.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.38,0:03:18.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头好疼 我这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.09,0:03:23.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听不见大家的声音了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.64,0:03:26.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.64,0:03:29.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵 不要勉强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.52,0:03:31.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢慢来就好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.35,0:03:35.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 确实是累了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.86,0:03:37.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为能更轻松一点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.82,0:03:40.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 很难走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.49,0:03:48.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头好疼 感觉非常的累 怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.12,0:03:50.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.33,0:03:51.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.04,0:03:55.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还差一点就到八合目了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.54,0:03:57.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再加一把劲 好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.59,0:04:07.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十合目之前 有八合目和本八合目对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.14,0:04:09.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵 要吃江米条吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.85,0:04:15.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑糖也有哦 还有羊羹 其实还有绿茶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.90,0:04:17.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爷爷么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.82,0:04:20.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.24,0:04:24.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我请工作人员刻了印 还有葵的那份
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.99,0:04:28.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说这个山间小屋圣德太子来过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.62,0:04:31.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 还有历史呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.79,0:04:35.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣德太子 似乎是骑着能飞天的马来的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.17,0:04:40.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太子真厉害 葵 说是骑着马来的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.67,0:04:43.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个水壶似乎是200年前的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.67,0:04:47.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,200年前是江户时代？葵 是不是很厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.60,0:04:52.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向 心夏 过来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.19,0:04:59.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们俩先去预约过的本八合目的山间小屋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.90,0:05:00.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.07,0:05:01.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.90,0:05:04.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是高山病呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.90,0:05:07.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在这先观察下她的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.95,0:05:09.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是没事的话 等下就过去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.96,0:05:17.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵 我们先走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.42,0:05:19.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好休息再过来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.92,0:05:21.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个 很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.84,0:05:24.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走了 枫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.38,0:05:26.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.72,0:05:27.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.26,0:05:27.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.64,0:05:32.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变成两个人了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.02,0:05:33.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.60,0:05:37.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵 明明那么干劲十足
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.02,0:05:41.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在向上面前进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.77,0:05:43.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算想也没有用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.69,0:05:46.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能拼命做现在能做的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.61,0:05:47.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.57,0:05:52.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵没事的 我们在本八合目等她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.41,0:05:52.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.08,0:06:01.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧 葵 要喝水吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.34,0:06:03.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.51,0:06:06.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头非常疼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.51,0:06:11.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向和心夏先出发了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.72,0:06:16.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为可以使用这里的山中小屋了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.18,0:06:18.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在里面躺着休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.81,0:06:22.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向她们走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.11,0:06:25.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办 完全没有变好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.53,0:06:28.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会变成这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.24,0:06:33.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相当难登呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.16,0:06:34.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.70,0:06:38.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明只是在走着 却像在跑一样上气不接下气
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.12,0:06:41.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然空气很稀薄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.63,0:06:43.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.38,0:06:47.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深呼吸就会好的 枫是这么说的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.84,0:06:49.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深呼吸？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.09,0:06:49.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.06,0:06:59.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有口哨也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.14,0:06:59.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,口哨？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.34,0:07:30.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是日向
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.80,0:07:34.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 平安到达了 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.77,0:07:43.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵就交给我 吃了饭好好休息哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.65,0:07:47.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果她没事的话 半夜我们就向山顶出发
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.11,0:07:52.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.28,0:07:57.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说是不用担心 身体好了之后半夜就会出发
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.49,0:07:58.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.12,0:08:01.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吃饭吧 肚子都饿扁了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.46,0:08:03.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.62,0:08:05.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.38,0:08:09.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.59,0:08:11.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的 好好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.98,0:08:27.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Excuse me（不好意思）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.07,0:08:32.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.12,0:08:46.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs42}现在开始的话看日出是不是勉强赶得上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.46,0:08:47.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs42}你以为是谁的错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.67,0:08:51.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.01,0:08:53.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在几点了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.84,0:08:56.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 差不多两点了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.22,0:08:57.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两点？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.35,0:08:59.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.22,0:09:04.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不抓紧的话 就赶不上去山顶看日出了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.85,0:09:06.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵 冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.90,0:09:07.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须要走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.06,0:09:08.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.15,0:09:12.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为 因为 我一直努力到这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.03,0:09:16.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要是勉强自己再走下去 如果回不去了怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.87,0:09:20.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山是不会逃走的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.41,0:09:22.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管多少次都可以挑战的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.00,0:09:23.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要急躁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.50,0:09:25.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.87,0:09:27.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.25,0:09:30.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再穿一件比较好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.59,0:09:31.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.01,0:09:35.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心夏 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.59,0:09:37.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是羊毛衫 很暖和哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.64,0:09:41.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下够了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.39,0:09:43.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都穿得好臃肿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.31,0:09:45.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.27,0:09:52.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是名片
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.27,0:09:54.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有很多职业的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.23,0:09:56.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有外国人的名片
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.24,0:09:57.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真壮观啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.07,0:10:00.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都爬到这里了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.99,0:10:03.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.54,0:10:06.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是枫发来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.08,0:10:08.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说让我们连葵的那份也要一起努力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.37,0:10:10.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.59,0:10:12.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.92,0:10:14.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连葵的那份一起登山吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.72,0:10:21.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好黑呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.35,0:10:24.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点可怕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.85,0:10:27.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和街上的黑完全不同呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.14,0:10:30.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是大自然的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.90,0:10:32.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs42}厕所募捐箱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.78,0:10:42.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点太悠闲了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.74,0:10:43.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么不好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.45,0:10:47.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.46,0:10:58.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真漂亮呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.05,0:10:59.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.01,0:11:02.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是葵也在看着就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.97,0:11:03.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.14,0:11:07.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是银河？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.77,0:11:13.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都想看的银河 和我想象的不同
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.52,0:11:16.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像斑点一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.15,0:11:26.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼吸很困难 但是情绪高涨 感觉不到疲惫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.75,0:11:30.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.62,0:11:34.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天空变得亮起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.04,0:11:36.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得抓紧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.34,0:11:38.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 就差一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.63,0:11:41.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 情绪高涨了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.13,0:11:43.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还差一点点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.43,0:11:45.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还差一点点了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.39,0:11:50.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想快点回去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.68,0:11:54.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是睡袋里 我想在床上好好地睡一觉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.82,0:11:59.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1200,0)\pos(142,435)}未完待续
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.55,0:08:18.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 你还记得那个人让你做那个吗？然后你说不要
